sg":"721 在各大媒體下都照講大話，狗官有冇睇新聞?<br />\n點解會覺得有媒體就唔會講大話?邏輯喺邊?理據喺邊?點撚樣證明有傳媒喺到就唔會講大話?"},{"pid":"69828dbd3372a1ca0b638480256172af5a4539d1","tid":2517111,"uid":275243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"杜酷刑靜左排又死撚返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n象牙塔高到去月球都唔敢認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28abcb916c40bc878abfcf9111c5dd21b7b9ffc2","tid":2517111,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"黑狗講咩都信嘅黑官"},{"pid":"97506350c8be46422bafe9715ed95169105c6a41","tid":2517111,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7892a04f5073bd7f6fa6065f616cd570c978b264","tid":2517111,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2eadd9ce0708667cca5cdd001098e64e9dd917","tid":2517111,"uid":235152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:27:55.000Z","msg":"佢意思班狗平時冇人影好多時有誣衊他人情況"},{"pid":"bc2344f1b173f68c8ae72c5c63324821822425b8","tid":2517111,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"最中意就係叫人唔好扮嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己就最撚扮嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4083324423ab7a367126de42935c0be2bf6eb97","tid":2517111,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"杜官訓左幾耐.....<br />\n<br />\n咁都難以想像?!?!"},{"pid":"671d98a302bff3f845c25ce34181a4f09410bedd","tid":2517111,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":