0505%2FIPNJDSBFA5AS3DVZO5RXTFEJYQ%2F&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=721ac56e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210505%2FIPNJDSBFA5AS3DVZO5RXTFEJYQ%2F&h=0a44e029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210505/IPNJDSBFA5AS3DVZO5RXTFEJYQ/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"&quot;<span class=\"red\">最終裁判官杜浩成推斷現場警員在高度警戒的狀態下，不可能在無緣無故被謾罵後誣衊被告無戴口罩</span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n定罪原來靠推斷就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74433e2a9aac837c1c933cd72e876d776f45870e","tid":2517111,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"已售出豬肉一舊"},{"pid":"71440bdec0ba8913b0628520a8bf3c1dd2fbfed0","tid":2517111,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4083324423ab7a367126de42935c0be2bf6eb97","tid":2517111,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:34:40.000Z","msg":"杜官訓左幾耐.....<br />\n<br />\n咁都難以想像?!?!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"杜浩成: 律政司不起訴示威者其他控罪決定奇怪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1995229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1995229</a><br />\n<br />\n聖誕德福廣場非法集結案 控方要求被告每週一次報到 杜浩成:案情嚴重 要求三次<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2098015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2098015</a><br />\n<br />\n兩中五生背囊被搜出酒精食用醋 杜浩成:需要加重保釋條件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2139263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2139263</a>"},{"pid":"d671f9919964b1ddcb98d639ed2d35554197641d","tid":2517111,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"///被告當時曾向警察叫喊「毅進仔、死黑警」。最終裁判官杜浩成推斷現場警員在高度警戒的狀態下，不可能在無緣無故被謾罵後誣衊被告無戴口罩///<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下乜撚野邏輯?<br />\n<br />\n果頭俾人鬧完<br />\n<br />\n轉過頭報復心態誣衊 先係常理啦好明顯? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.hkgo